wiki.summary: “Players” is a single by American rapper and singer Coi Leray, released on November 30, 2022 via Republic Records. Over a sample of “The Message” by Grandmaster Flash & Furious Five, Coi Leray rips through one bold and braggadocious bar after another, exuding confidence and charisma. It pops off with the instantly unshakable hook as she proves, “‘Cause girls is players too.” She teased a snippet on TikTok, and it instantly attracted over five million views and counting. Read more on Last.fm.
